<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>ACCESS_GRANTED: DADA_BDAY_2026</title>
    <style>
        body { background-color: #0c0c0c; color: #00ff41; font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; padding: 50px; }
        .terminal { border: 2px solid #00ff41; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 0 0 15px #00ff41; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; }
        h1 { font-size: 1.5em; border-bottom: 1px solid #00ff41; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        .blink { animation: blinker 1s linear infinite; }
        @keyframes blinker { 50% { opacity: 0; } }
        .log-entry { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .command { color: #ffffff; }
        
        /* Styles for the button */
        #secretButton {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 1px solid #00ff41;
            color: #00ff41;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        #secretButton:hover {
            background-color: #00ff41;
            color: #0c0c0c;
        }
        /* Style for the hidden message */
        #hiddenMessage {
            display: none; /* Initially hide the message */
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 1px dashed #00ff41;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="terminal">
        <h1>> SYSTEM_INITIALIZING...</h1>
        <p class="log-entry"><span class="command">C:\Users\Dad></span> run birthday_wish.exe</p>
        <p class="log-entry">Searching for memories... [OK]</p>
        <p class="log-entry">Loading Dad Jokes database... [OK]</p>
        <hr>
        <h2>HAPPY BIRTHDAY, DAD!</h2>
        <p>From Scratch projects to University, thanks for being my favorite mentor.</p>
        <p class="log-entry"><strong>> MESSAGE:</strong> "I know you said don't spend a dime, so I spent some lines of code instead."</p>
        <hr>
        
        <p class="log-entry"><span class="command">C:\Users\Dad></span> <button id="secretButton">> Read Secret Log</button></p>
        
        <div id="hiddenMessage">
            <p><strong>LOG_ENTRY://MEMORIES_VAULT_DECRYPTED</strong></p>
            <p>
               Hallo Dada, ich habe versucht eine Webseite für dich zu kodieren!
            </p>
        </div>

        <p class="log-entry"><span class="command">C:\Users\Dad></span> <span class="blink">_</span></p>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('secretButton').addEventListener('click', function() {
            var message = document.getElementById('hiddenMessage');
            if (message.style.display === 'none') {
                message.style.display = 'block'; // Show it!
            } else {
                message.style.display = 'none'; // Hide it if they click again!
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
